  RFC8780 [label="RFC8780
The Path Computation Element
Communication Protocol (PCEP) Extension
for Wavelength Switched Optical Network
(WSON) Routing and Wavelength Assignment
(RWA)
2020", shape=ellipse, fillcolor="#e8f0ff", tooltip="This document provides Path Computation Element Communication Protocol (PCEP) extensions for the support of Routing and Wavelength Assignment (RWA) in Wavelength Switched Optical Networks (WSONs).  Path provisioning in WSONs requires an RWA process.  From a path computation perspective, wavelength assignment is the process of determining which wavelength can be used on each hop of a path and forms an additional routing constraint to optical path computation.", style=filled, fillcolor=green]; 

